The <a
href="https://news.opensuse.org/2025/10/01/next-chapter-opens-with-leap-release/">openSUSE
Leap 16 release</a> is now available.
<p>
<blockquote class="bq">
	This major version update of our fixed-release community-Linux
	distribution has a fresh software stack and introduces an unmatched
	maintenance- and security-support cycle, a new installer and
	simplified migration options.
</blockquote>
<p>
See <a href="https://lwn.net/Articles/1019688/">our look at this release</a> for more
information.